{"tid":2061971,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【瞄準中國?】美海軍陸戰隊新兵團 擬駐軍日本沖繩","createTime":"2020-06-12T19:27:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T03:20:18.000Z","uid":141151,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0934681db1ce3ab335df8b92ff19a0bf2668f169","tid":2061971,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T19:27:19.000Z","msg":"【瞄準中國?】美海軍陸戰隊新兵團 擬駐軍日本沖繩<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200613/4WEZRF2N7NAQD5RBKJ4UARUIPA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200613%2F4WEZRF2N7NAQD5RBKJ4UARUIPA%2F&d=q8peb0UcLz3Z6%2FQAtnUTjMF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=20cba12d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200613%2F4WEZRF2N7NAQD5RBKJ4UARUIPA%2F&h=a35b277e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200613/4WEZRF2N7NAQD5RBKJ4UARUIPA/</a><br />\n<br />\n日本《共同社》報道，美國海軍陸戰隊計劃創設的「海軍陸戰隊瀕海作戰團」(Marine Littoral Regiment, MLR)，會先在美國夏威夷成團，然後會探討派駐關島及日本。日本的駐地預料會在沖繩，並編入設置了司令部的海軍陸戰隊第三遠征軍。整支 MLR 的兵員數目預計會有1,800人至2,200人。<br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n全文請前往蘋果日報"},{"pid":"6fc33754db03954cd9221aea2503984706a1a1a5","tid":2061971,"uid":261914,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T19:31:20.000Z","msg":"建立一支機動能力強、配備導彈及火箭炮、並由無人機等高科技武器支援的快速應變部隊<br />\n<br />\ndivision<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c63309403b6472bf69459ae95438d5a2233a1347","tid":2061971,"uid":45977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T19:31:49.000Z","msg":"比香港人加入啦"},{"pid":"db04801565171319df3d24f2ca2614cc16fe5395","tid":2061971,"uid":94828,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T19:37:20.000Z","msg":"琉球人真陰公"},{"pid":"caa8cb89168a49d2b45002d8247a3bf0fa18aec8","tid":2061971,"uid":249708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T19:40:03.000Z","msg":"突發！昂船洲要人